sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Vendor
    participant Portal as Vendor Portal
    participant API as Backend API
    participant VendorSvc as Vendor Submission Service
    participant Project as Project Service
    participant Storage as File Storage
    participant DB as Application Database
    participant Audit as Audit Log

    Vendor->>Portal: Enter PO number
    Portal->>API: Verify PO number
    API->>VendorSvc: Check PO eligibility
    VendorSvc->>Project: Load project by PO number
    Project->>DB: Read project and PO status
    DB-->>Project: Project and PO data
    Project-->>VendorSvc: PO verification result

    alt PO invalid or closed
        VendorSvc-->>API: Reject submission
        API-->>Portal: Return invalid PO message
        Portal-->>Vendor: Show rejection message
    else PO valid and open
        VendorSvc-->>API: Allow upload
        API-->>Portal: Return upload form
        Vendor->>Portal: Upload delivery document
        Portal->>API: Submit delivery file
        API->>VendorSvc: Validate file and submission data
        VendorSvc->>Storage: Save delivery file
        Storage-->>VendorSvc: Stored file path
        VendorSvc->>DB: Create vendor submission record
        DB-->>VendorSvc: Submission saved
        VendorSvc->>Audit: Record vendor submission event
        Audit->>DB: Save audit log entry
        DB-->>Audit: Audit saved
        VendorSvc-->>API: Return submission result
        API-->>Portal: Return success response
        Portal-->>Vendor: Show submission confirmation
    end
